#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Main menu item
#: ../iso-scan.templates:4
msgid "Scan hard drives for an installer ISO image"
msgstr "Chwilio disgiau caled am ddelwedd ISO sefydlydd"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../iso-scan.templates:8
msgid "stable, testing, unstable"
msgstr "sefydlog,profi,ansefydlog"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:9
msgid "Debian version to install:"
msgstr "Y fersiwn o Debian i sefydlu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:9
msgid ""
"Debian comes in several flavors. Stable is well-tested and rarely changes. "
"Unstable is untested and frequently changing. Testing is a middle ground, "
"that receives many of the new versions from unstable if they are not too "
"buggy."
msgstr ""
"Mae Debian ar gael mewn sawl blas. Mae \"sefydlog\" wedi ei brofi'n drwyadl "
"ac yn newid yn anaml. Mae \"ansefydlog\" heb ei brofi ac yn newid yn aml.Mae "
"\"profi\" rhwng y ddau, gan dderbyn nifer o fersiynau newydd o \"ansefydlog"
"\" os nad oes ganddynt gormod o namau."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:17
msgid "Detecting hardware to find hard drives"
msgstr "Yn chwilio am galedwedd er mwyn canfod disgiau caled"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:21
msgid "Searching drives for an installer ISO image"
msgstr "Yn chwilio disgiau am ddelwedd ISO sefydlydd"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:25
msgid "Mounting ${DRIVE}..."
msgstr "Yn clymu ${DRIVE}..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:29
msgid "Scanning ${DRIVE} (in ${DIRECTORY})..."
msgstr "Yn chwilio ${DRIVE} (yn ${DIRECTORY})..."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:34
msgid "Do full disk search for installer ISO image?"
msgstr "Gwneud chwiliad disg llawn am ddelwedd ISO sefydlydd?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:34
msgid ""
"The quick scan for installer ISO images, which looks only in common places, "
"did not find an installer ISO image. It's possible that a more thorough "
"search will find the ISO image, but it may take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Ni wnaeth y chwiliad cyflym am ddelweddau sefydlydd ISO, sydd ond yn edrych "
"mewn llefydd cyffredin, ganfod delwedd ISO sefydlydd. Mae'n bosib y bydd "
"chwiliad mwy trwyadl yn canfod y delwedd ISO, ond gall gymryd amser hir."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:42
msgid ""
"No installer ISO images were found. If you downloaded the ISO image, it may "
"have a bad filename (not ending in \".iso\"), or it may be on a file system "
"that could not be mounted. You'll have to do a network install instead, or "
"reboot and fix the ISO image."
msgstr ""
"Ni chanfuwyd unrhyw ddelweddau ISO sefydlydd. Os lawrlwythoch y delwedd ISO, "
"efallai bod ganddo enw ffeil gwael (nad yw'n gorffen yn \".iso\"), neu gall "
"fod ar system ffeiliau ni allwyd clymu. Bydd rhaid i chi wneud sefydliad "
"rhwydwaith yn lle, neu ailfŵtio a thrwsio'r delwedd ISO."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:50
msgid "Failed to find an installer ISO image"
msgstr "Methwyd canfod delwedd ISO sefydlydd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:50
msgid ""
"While one or more possible ISO images were found, they could not be mounted. "
"The ISO image you downloaded may be corrupt."
msgstr ""
"Er canfuwyd un neu fwy delwedd ISO posib, methwyd eu clymu. Efallai bo'r "
"delwedd ISO lawrlwythoch yn llygredig."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:58
msgid "No installer ISO image found"
msgstr "Ni chanfuwyd delwedd ISO sefydlydd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:58
msgid ""
"While one or more possible ISO images were found, they did not look like "
"valid installer ISO images."
msgstr ""
"Er canfuwyd un neu fwy delwedd ISO posib, nid oeddent yn edrydd fel "
"delweddau ISO sefydlydd dilys."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:58
msgid "Please do a network install instead, or reboot and fix the ISO image."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, gwnewch sefydliad rhwyswaith yn lle, neu ailfŵtiwch a "
"thrwsio'r delwedd ISO."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:66
msgid "Successfully mounted ${SUITE} installer ISO image"
msgstr "Clymwyd delwedd ISO sefydlydd ${SUITE}"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../iso-scan.templates:66
msgid ""
"The ISO file ${FILENAME} on ${DEVICE} (${SUITE}) will be used as the "
"installation ISO image."
msgstr ""
"Caiff y ffeil ISO ${FILENAME} ar ${DEVICE} (${SUITE}) ei ddefnyddio fel y y "
"ddelwedd ISO sefydlu."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Main menu item
#: ../load-iso.templates:4
msgid "Load installer components from an installer ISO"
msgstr "Llwytho cydrannau sefydlydd o ISO sefydlydd"
